1
00:00:00,313 --> 00:00:05,000
Unit 18 Lesson 35
第十八单元  第三十五课

2
00:00:05,106 --> 00:00:07,926
Men can cook, too! 
男人也能做饭

3
00:00:07,976 --> 00:00:10,073
Let's cook dinner, Robert. 
我们来做饭吧  罗伯特

4
00:00:10,153 --> 00:00:11,786
You can help me. 
你来帮我忙吧

5
00:00:12,176 --> 00:00:14,846
Give me some rice, please. 
给我点米

6
00:00:15,080 --> 00:00:17,923
There's some rice in that jar. 
米在那个罐子里

7
00:00:18,006 --> 00:00:20,266
Put some water in the pan, 
在平底锅里放点水

8
00:00:20,323 --> 00:00:22,703
and pass me a knife, please.
然后把刀递给我

9
00:00:22,976 --> 00:00:24,496
Which one?
哪把刀

10
00:00:24,566 --> 00:00:26,506
That one on the table.
桌子上的那把

11
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:29,536
OK, Dad. Here it is.
好的  爸爸  给你

12
00:00:29,796 --> 00:00:32,763
Chop two onions, please.
切两个洋葱

13
00:00:32,783 --> 00:00:35,823
OK, Dad. Chop two onions...
好的  爸爸  切两个洋葱

14
00:00:36,070 --> 00:00:39,083
Is there a big spoon over there?
那边有个大勺子吗

15
00:00:39,206 --> 00:00:40,956
Yes, Dad.
是的  爸爸

16
00:00:41,020 --> 00:00:43,506
Pass me the big spoon, please.
把那个大勺子给我

17
00:00:43,586 --> 00:00:45,156
I can't get a spoon.
爸爸  我不能又拿勺子

18
00:00:45,180 --> 00:00:47,306
and chop an onion, Dad!
又切洋葱

19
00:00:47,370 --> 00:00:48,830
You're right. 
说的对

20
00:00:48,896 --> 00:00:51,446
What about some plates?
那边有盘子吗

21
00:00:51,763 --> 00:00:54,783
Dad, there are some plates on the shelf.
爸爸  架子上有盘子

22
00:00:54,863 --> 00:00:56,186
There are some knives, 
抽屉里还有刀叉

23
00:00:56,190 --> 00:00:59,110
some forks and some spoons in the drawer. 
和汤匙

24
00:00:59,463 --> 00:01:02,040
And my hands are wet.
我的手湿了

25
00:01:02,316 --> 00:01:03,570
You see, Robert, 
你看  罗伯特   

26
00:01:03,623 --> 00:01:05,563
men can cook, too. 
男人也可以做饭

27
00:01:05,620 --> 00:01:08,053
Perhaps we can open a restaurant!
也许我们可以开家饭馆

28
00:01:08,493 --> 00:01:10,653
Oh, yeah!
哦  是的

